message.body: Safe travels this morning my small one! Thank you so much for coming down this weekend, it was sooo good to get to spend some time with you!! Love you!!!
Oh thank you!!!!! Glad I could come!! Very very good to see you - sorry I was such a zombie yesterday! Love you!
Haha no worries, I was a total zombie too!!!
Haha have a good day at work! Hope you got to sleep!!
Thank you!! I did, I slept like 9 hours but I still feel totally sleepy haha...maybe I'll hop into the respite for a nap today...
